'''"The Times and Trepidations of Majnar Roak"''' was an animated [[holostrip]] syndicated by [[Sektor 242 NewsLine]]. It was one of the ten most popular animated holostrips in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]].

"Roak" concerned itself with the problems of a retiring finance clerk living on a backwater [[Planet/Legends|world]], though it was also at times a satire of the [[Sarin sector/Legends|Sarin sector]]. At any given time could be difficult to tell which it was, and the strip was described as "bewildering."

